&lt;p&gt;This is a strong fit for someone who enjoys digging into AWS console errors, tracing IAM denials, untangling Terraform state, and tuning the database or deployment path behind a production slowdown. At the L3 end of the band, this person will increasingly lead well-scoped platform initiatives while staying close to the operational craft.&lt;/p&gt;
