&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic conversations with C-level executives and senior decision-makers across lending, operations, and technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct rigorous discovery to understand each institution’s portfolio composition, draw-administration process, and operational pain points.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quantify Built’s impact through ROI modeling and workflow analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Marketing, Product, and Client Success to align messaging, demo strategy, and post-sale delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diligently build and manage pipeline, maintaining accurate forecasts and CRM hygiene.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Built at industry conferences and client events, strengthening relationships and uncovering new opportunities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
