&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built Technologies is the AI-first platform for construction and real estate finance, managing over $300 billion in annual capital for more than 340 lenders — including 45 of the top 100 U.S. banks. The FP&amp;amp;A team provides the financial intelligence that enables Built to grow with discipline: the forecasting, modeling, and analytical frameworks that help the CEO, CFO, and business leaders understand performance, allocate capital, and make consequential decisions with confidence. In a multi-product SaaS business operating across Lender, Owner, Contractor, and Marketplace segments, the financial complexity that FP&amp;amp;A manages is substantial — and the stakes are real.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The FP&amp;amp;A Analyst is an entry-level role designed for someone building their foundation in corporate finance. You will support Built’s Finance team in delivering financial reporting, budgeting, and analytical work that helps the business understand its performance and make informed decisions — developing the skills, systems knowledge, and business acumen that define a strong FP&amp;amp;A career.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Guiding Principles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
